ational_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4696, \"end\": 4703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9999989060058014, \"rank\": 1.0939704684306195e-06, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With each team picking two men and two women, the U.S. and China both went with their male swimmers in the first two legs.\", \"from\": 4784, \"to\": 4906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4843, \"end\": 4848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8869882036796406, \"rank\": 0.1267055548647154, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murphy put the U.S. in front on the backstroke, China's Qin Haiyang slipped past Nic Fink on the breaststroke, but Walsh put the Americans back in front on the butterfly before Huske held off Yang Junxuan to secure the gold.\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 5132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4956, \"end\": 4961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8869882036796406, \"rank\": 0.1267055548647154, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4964, \"end\": 4975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"score\": 0.9999938624998401, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Qin Haiyang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbp