, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.4765729991739313, \"rank\": 0.6955741343828152, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchand swam the breaststroke leg for France but could not add to his already impressive haul of four individual golds.\", \"from\": 5264, \"to\": 5384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5303, \"end\": 5309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.730202677419144, \"rank\": 0.30363080504930784, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French finished fourth, more than two seconds behind the Aussies.\", \"from\": 5385, \"to\": 5454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5389, \"end\": 5395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.4729115920216755, \"rank\": 0.7364904166556492, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the British won gold in 2021, the Americans finished fifth.\", \"from\": 5456, \"to\": 5520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5465, \"end\": 5472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9166932556923, \"rank\": 0.09087297955702033, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain was seventh this time.\", \"from\": 5521, \"to\": 5551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5521, \"end\": 5528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9999989060058014, \"rank\": 1.09397