team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5800, \"end\": 5804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9444132489815691, \"rank\": 0.05884009967417597, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mil\\u00e1k had failed to defend his Olympic title in the 200 butterfly, settling for a silver behind French star Marchand.\", \"from\": 5863, \"to\": 5980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5959, \"end\": 5965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.4729115920216755, \"rank\": 0.7364904166556492, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mil\\u00e1k claimed silver in the 100 fly three years ago, but he did not have to worry about the guy who beat him in that race.\", \"from\": 5982, \"to\": 6104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"American Caeleb Dressel stunningly failed to qualify for the final, posting only the 13th-fastest time in the semifinals Friday.\", \"from\": 6105, \"to\": 6233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6105, \"end\": 6113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997729723168655, \"rank\": 0.00022471055462751276, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 6114, \"end\": 6128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caeleb Dressel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\"}]}, {\"sentence